songs.title: We Can’t Fly - Oliver Remix
songs.lyrics:
We can fly, come on, let's try
We're boys and girls, who rule the world
We can fly or kiss the sky
So long, bye, bye

We can't, oh, oh, we can
We can't, oh, oh, we can
We can't, oh, oh, we can
We can't, oh, oh, we can

We can fly, come on, let's try
We're boys and girls, who rule the world
We can fly or kiss the sky
So long, bye, bye

Come on, don't cry
We can fly, come on, let's try
We're boys and girls
Who rule the world
